name: UFO War (indravb6)
description:
Grog is an alien, his race wants to rule the earth because it has rich resources. in 2050, his race went to earth to kill all mankind. but Grog feels sorry for humans because they don't do anything wrong. finally Grog dared to fight his own race in order to protect humans.
